"If this be their true interest, have they in fact pursued it?",1,0,0,0,0,0
"Has it not, on the contrary, invariably been found that momentary passions, and immediate interest, have a more active and imperious control over human conduct than general or remote considerations of policy, utility or justice?",0,0,0,0,0,0
