"Let experience, the least fallible guide of human opinions, be appealed to for an answer to these inquiries.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"Sparta, Athens, Rome, and Carthage were all republics; two of them, Athens and Carthage, of the commercial kind.",1,0,0,0,0,0
